promptPrefix:
Prompt text including placeholders [TARGETLANGUAGE], [PROMPT], [VARIABLE1], [VARIABLE2] and [VARIABLE3] replaced automagically by MKT18

[VARIABLE], [VARIABLE2] and [VARIABLE3] require title with optional default value and available values.

Example: Example[PROMPT] in [TARGETLANGUAGE] with [VARIABLE1], [VARIABLE2] and [VARIABLE3].
[VARIABLE1: Title] [VARIABLE2:Title:DefaultValue]
[VARIABLE3:Title:DefaultValue:Available Value 1|Available Value 2|Available Value 3].

[VARIABLE1], [VARIABLE2] and [VARIABLE3] will be pre-filled using URL parameters AIPRM_VARIABLE1, AIPRM_VARIABLE2 and AIPRM_VARIABLE3
